## import 组织

**三段式分组**，用空行分隔：

```go
import (
    // 1. 标准库
    "context"
    "fmt"

    // 2. 第三方库
    "github.com/bytedance/sonic"
    "github.com/samber/lo"
    "go.uber.org/zap"

    // 3. 项目内部包
    "github.com/hcd233/aris-proxy-api/internal/dto"
    "github.com/hcd233/aris-proxy-api/internal/service"
)
```

- 包路径有冲突时使用别名导入：`dbmodel "...database/model"`、`objdao "...storage/obj_dao"`

